precis:
Amendments to the FISHERY (GENERAL) REGULATIONS which are largely
housekeeping measures and touch upon matters such as notifying the public
about variation orders, the placement of vessel registration numbers, gear
retrieval prior to inspection, and marking requirements for buoys.
